Introductory review section of PhD thesis in Theoretical Physics at
  the Oskar Klein Centre for Cosmoparticle Physics, Stockholm University;
  defended June 7, 2011. 174 pages; ISBN 978-91-7447-312-4

column11:
  Compilation of the papers contributed by the MAGIC collaboration to the 32nd
International Cosmic Ray Conference (ICRC 2011), which took place between
August 11 and 18, 2011 in Beijing, China. The papers are sorted in 6
categories: Overview and Highlight papers; Instrument, software and techniques;
Galactic sources; Extragalactic sources; Multi-wavelength and joint campaigns;
Fundamental physics, dark matter and cosmic rays.
